                The number <m>12345_8</m> can be expanded in base 8 as <m>1\times 8^4+2\times 8^3+3\times 8^2+4\times 8^1+5\times 8^0</m>.  Expand the following numbers into base 8 in a similar fashion.  Then perform the resulting calculation to find the expression of each in decimal form.
