                    <m>210_3=2\times 3^2+1\times 3^1+0\times 3^0=18+3+0=21</m>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <m>11001_2=1\times 2^4+1\times 2^3+0\times 2^2+0\times 2^1+1\times 2^0=16+8+0+0+1=25</m>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <m>4135_6=4\times 6^3+1\times 6^2+3\times 6^1+5\times 6^0=864+36+18+5=923</m>
